Goliath Gold to Close Underground Training Operations Due to Rising Water

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-06-08T05:51:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/goliath-gold-to-close-underground-training-operations-due-to-rising-water.html
Goliath Gold Mining Ltd. said it will
temporarily close its underground training center at Sub Nigel 1
because of rising water levels.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
